Class MySet<E>

java.lang.Object

public class MySet<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements interfaces.MyList<E>
A simple MySet class defining MySet objects (generic implementation of a Set). Class based on Programming Patterns' Assignment 02 (Java Generics - MySet). Class based on MyLinkedList from Programming Patterns' Lab 02.
Author:
Giuliana Bouzon
